    "[91] Proposes a driver distraction detection system using a blend of deep learning and machine learning models, relevant for enhancing roadway safety through distraction monitoring.",
    "DenseNet and Genetic Algorithms (GA)TCombines DenseNet and GA for driver distraction detection, focusing on posture-based insights for safety in autonomous vehicles.",
    "[76] Leverages MobileNetV2 for efficient classification of driver distraction behaviors, demonstrating potential for reducing accidents caused by distracted driving in autonomous vehicles.",
    "MobileNetV2MobileNetV2 classifies driver distractions by detecting subtle posture changes, aiding vision systems in autonomous vehicles.joint angle profiles for various walking speeds and slopes, minimizing input data requirements.",
